Spring dataJpa

Add dependency
- Write appropriate properties in application.properties file
- Annotate entity/Model class with appropriate calsses
- Write an interface, and extends JpaRepository


Spring Data JPA gives build in interface like JpaRepository which we need to extend in our old 
This interface gives us build in methods for CURD operations
We don't have to write implementation to this interface


